<section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
  <div class="flex items-start gap-6" data-aos="fade-up">
    <img src="{{ site.author.avatar }}" alt="avatar" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full object-cover" />
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">{{ site.author.name }}</h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">{{ site.author.bio }}</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">坐标：{{ site.author.location }}</p>
      <div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-4">
        <a href="{{ site.social.github }}" class="hover:text-livingCoral">GitHub</a>
        <a href="{{ site.social.email }}" class="hover:text-livingCoral">邮箱</a>
        <a href="{{ site.social.weibo }}" class="hover:text-livingCoral">微博</a>
        <a href="{{ site.social.bilibili }}" class="hover:text-livingCoral">B站</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="prose prose-neutral dark:prose-invert mt-10" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
    <h2>本站</h2>
    <p>这是一个使用 <strong>Eleventy</strong> 和 <strong>Tailwind CSS</strong> 构建的现代化静态博客，主题色为 <span class="brand">Living Coral</span>。</p>
    <ul>
      <li>暗黑模式一键切换</li>
      <li>支持分类、标签与相关文章</li>
      <li>适配移动端，加载迅速</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>


